item.description:
Come join us for a cup of tea and lively conversation.
We are not a political group, but this week's inauguration just seems too monumental to skip over. By this time the United States will have a new President. What does this mean to you and to the world? We have many members who come from many different countries. It would be interesting to hear their perspectives. If anyone has a French-language newspaper article about the election, please bring it with you.

group.name: The West Hartford Groupe de French
